# Hirebuddy Job Board

A modern job board web application with AI-powered resume features, built using Flask (Python) for the backend and HTML/CSS/JS for the frontend.

---

## Features

- **Job Search:** Search and filter jobs by title or description.
- **Responsive UI:** Clean, mobile-friendly design.
- **Slideshow Banner:** Eye-catching image slider at the top.
- **AI Resume Tools:** (Planned/Optional) Integrate AI for resume parsing or suggestions.
- **Easy Apply:** Direct application links for jobs.
- **Full-Text Search:** Fast job search using SQLite FTS.

---

## Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Backend:** Python, Flask, SQLite
- **Deployment:**  
  - Frontend: [Vercel](https://vercel.com) or [Netlify](https://netlify.com)  
  - Backend: [Render](https://render.com), [Railway](https://railway.app), [Fly.io](https://fly.io), or [Heroku](https://heroku.com)

